{"tid":2302506,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"臺籍中國人黃安又急了","createTime":"2020-11-27T07:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T11:54:22.000Z","uid":90457,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"509d5906545b149b626cf170515a9e8c17f5d620","tid":2302506,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:15:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=855319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D855319&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpO%2FcXzH0lQqBACTLtzCSRXY%3D&h=047121e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D855319&h=cc71b7a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=855319</a><br />\n<br />\n擬祭「黃安條款」！無法再爽用健保　黃安氣炸喊拆總統府<br />\n2020/11/27 07:49<br />\n娛樂中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n長期住在中國大陸的57歲資深藝人黃安，因多次表達對「祖國」的認同，甚至自詡「台獨剋星」，大肆批評台灣藝人的「台獨言行」而引起公憤，但他每回生病時總會回台灣使用健保看病，讓長期旅外的國人享有台灣健保資源的議題浮上檯面，健保署也擬修法，將針對旅外國人停復保制度進行修正，此舉卻讓黃安相當不滿，重砲狂轟民進黨政府。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TgWPSF8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTgWPSF8.jpg&h=81474df1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲自詡「台獨剋星」的黃安旅居中國多年。（圖／翻攝自黃安微博）<br />\n<br />\n健保財務吃緊，傳出健保費率可能調漲，且為了遏止「黃安們」防用健保資源，健保署也擬修法針對旅外國人停復保制度進行修正，未來將可能取消出國6個月至2年短期停復保規定，出國逾2年者已除籍退保者，則必須等待半年或繳清出國期間保費才可納保，最多可追討5年保費，因此長年旅居中國的黃安未來也恐怕被追討保費。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY9ejk5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY9ejk5.jpg&h=2f215daa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲黃安對健保費調漲相當不滿。（圖／翻攝自黃安微博）<br />\n<br />\n對此，黃安相當不滿，在微博發文重砲抨擊：「我黃某人爽用健康保險，健保費就要漲？還追討？很棒呀！我黃安也爽遊台北故宮，故宮票價漲不？我曾爽遊『總統府』，總統府拆不？」字裡行間盡是氣憤，最後更嗆民進黨政府，要政府乾脆立法「不爽民進黨者，不得爽用健保」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea5568456b56d7d6d9fffaa0215e694cac871ef","tid":2302506,"uid":160592,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:19:04.000Z","msg":"有著數時<br />\n又突然是台灣人了"},{"pid":"7550ec3df931936cb6fce5829658dd1369789fcf","tid":2302506,"uid":40267,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:20:21.000Z","msg":"用五險一金囉柒頭皮"},{"pid":"78c2080a78b4d8721fdd3eabc87ac0dc5f3c0d53","tid":2302506,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8cc255e4610b67e17208d940b782cbe6d8bb52","tid":2302506,"uid":185656,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:26:32.000Z","msg":"去北京醫啦,冇得研究你身體係臺灣損失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086c02f9317d86cf3837da03bd846c8151dfcad5","tid":2302506,"uid":183844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:29:25.000Z","msg":"九唔搭八<br />\n有愛支病都係怪怪地"},{"pid":"7d990fc37bee98f1d6fc8274db30461d5e38de71","tid":2302506,"uid":200083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:30:43.000Z","msg":"做個堂堂正正中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d29fb7c388026fbc55ea705cb4352abbdfeabd","tid":2302506,"uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:31:35.000Z","msg":"冇供款都可以用？"},{"pid":"2300a9b2a2feb7a8489631dba49a7c8ffc1afd15","tid":2302506,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:32:19.000Z","msg":"好心唔好再返台灣啦"},{"pid":"4434d344588b79f1e25846340ca783e4b001a053","tid":2302506,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:33:25.000Z","msg":"中國咁好唔